Donadoni to @Radio1Rai: &quot;When will I coach Milan? One day, I hope. But it does not only depend on me. There must be a departure of someone else [the manager], but It seems to me that Milan are now recovering after a difficult start to the season.&quot;<br />
<br />
Donadoni: &quot;I hope that Gattuso can get many successive victories, because he has a team that can fight for the top positions. When will I be back on the bench? I have no frenzy, but I want to go back to coaching soon.&quot;
